'''保護國界有功獎章'''（{{lang-ru|'''Медаль «За отличие в охране государственной границы»'''}}；[[英文|英文]]：'''Medal "For Distinction in the Protection of the State Borders"'''），是[[俄羅斯聯邦|俄羅斯聯邦]]頒發的一項[[獎章|獎章]]，演化自[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]時代的[[守卫苏联国界有功奖章|守卫苏联国界有功奖章]]。

== 歷史 ==
保護國界有功獎章於1994年3月2日通過[[總統令|總統令]]設立<ref name="decree442">{{cite web | author = Russian Government | title = Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of March 2, 1994 No 442 | publisher = Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards | date = 1999-12-15 | url = http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u442.htm | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205195909/http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u442.htm | archivedate = 2012-02-05 }}</ref>，頒發章程曾分別在1999年1月6日<ref name="decree19">{{cite web | author = Russian Government | title = Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of March 6, 1999 No 19 | publisher = Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards | date = 1999-12-15 | url = http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u19.htm | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205195833/http://award.adm.gov.ru/doc/u19.htm | archivedate = 2012-02-05 }}</ref>和2010年9月7日<ref name="decree1099">{{cite web | author = Russian Government | title = Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of September 7, 2010 No 1099 | publisher = Russian Gazette | date = 2010-09-07 | url = http://www.rg.ru/2010/09/15/nagrady-dok.html | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | archive-date = 2016-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310205827/http://rg.ru/2010/09/15/nagrady-dok.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>兩度通過總統令進行修訂。在2010年的修訂中，頒發章程和獎章外貌被大幅改動<ref name="decree1099" />，以凸顯出與蘇聯獎勵系統的區別。
== 頒發 == 
保護國界有功獎章是頒發給在戰爭或特別任務中參與邊防服務，保護俄羅斯聯邦的國家邊界，在其中顯出勇氣、領導和獻身精神的俄羅斯[[軍人|軍人]]及公民<ref name="statute">{{cite web | author = Russian Government | title = Statute of the Medal "For Distinction in Protection of the State Borders" | publisher = Commission under the President of the Russian Federation on state awards | date = 2010-09-07 | url = http://award.gov.ru/border_medal.html | language = ru | accessdate = 2012-02-15 | archive-date = 2011-12-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111207065255/http://award.gov.ru/border_medal.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。受勳者應把勳章戴在胸部的左邊，並且要和[[維持秩序有功獎章|維持秩序有功獎章]]放在一起<ref name="decree1099" />。

== 獎章外貌 ==
保護國界有功獎章為一圓形銀牌，直徑長32mm，邊緣凸起<ref name="statute"/>。獎章正面印有[[俄羅斯聯邦國徽|俄羅斯聯邦國徽]]，底部則有[[棕櫚|棕櫚]]和[[月桂|月桂]]的樹枝，中央有兩把交疊的[[劍|劍]]<ref name="statute"/>；反面印有一行字“保護國界有功”（[[俄語|俄語]]：ЗА ОТЛИЧИЕ В ОХРАНЕ ГОСУДАРСТВЕННОЙ ГРАНИЦЫ），底部有一條預留用作填上序號的橫線<ref name="statute"/>。 

保護國界有功獎章的綬帶為一[[五邊形|五邊形]]，上有一條24毫米寬的綠色條紋，左右均有3mm的紅色條紋<ref name="statute"/>。

